JOHANNESBURG – The now wedded Mr and Mrs Managa went through ups and downs before they joined in holy matrimony. Hope, the wife of Moses, confessed that she cheated on her husband. Twitter is abuzz because in this episode of Our Perfect wedding the wedded women was the unfaithful one in the relationship. Hope claimed that their long distance arrangement at the time was causing strain on their relationship.  READ: Trevor Gumbi shocks Instagram with divorce post The Tshivenda couple got married despite the wife's pervious infidelity because she claims that she stepped out of their relationship to get her husband's attention. There have been mixed reactions about her confession: some claim that it is a good strategy because the outcome was marriage, while others think that going to the extreme measures of cheathing will not work for all relationships.